    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Order of insects containing 2,400 species and about 430 genera in 15 families, found in temperate and tropical habitats globally.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
